Ten minutes.

1689
01:53:28,640 --> 01:53:29,880
Officer Wong? Under 5 minutes.

1690
01:53:35,280 --> 01:53:37,200
We've tapped Qiuguo's phone.

1691
01:53:37,400 --> 01:53:38,520
Copy. Copy.

1692
01:53:42,640 --> 01:53:43,560
Sound check.

1693
01:53:43,600 --> 01:53:44,840
Loud and clear.

1694
01:53:45,760 --> 01:53:47,680
Wang is already 10 minutes late.

1695
01:53:47,880 --> 01:53:48,960
He'll leave at any moment.

1696
01:53:56,840 --> 01:53:57,840
He's leaving.

1697
01:54:03,640 --> 01:54:04,720
Customers are off limits.

1698
01:54:04,840 --> 01:54:05,960
Please use the front door.

1699
01:54:25,320 --> 01:54:26,400
Small world.

1700
01:54:37,560 --> 01:54:38,560
Alone?

1701
01:54:42,720 --> 01:54:43,920
You have the wrong person.

1702
01:54:46,640 --> 01:54:47,680
You don't know me?

1703
01:54:50,240 --> 01:54:51,480
We had dinner together.

1704
01:54:52,280 --> 01:54:53,440
Forgotten me already?

1705
01:54:57,920 --> 01:54:59,120
Do you need something?

1706
01:55:10,360 --> 01:55:12,320
I'm so moved.

1707
01:55:13,480 --> 01:55:14,760
It's you. Uncle.

1708
01:55:15,160 --> 01:55:16,240
What's with the outfit?

1709
01:55:16,320 --> 01:55:18,240
That hair of yours freaked me out.

1710
01:55:18,520 --> 01:55:20,080
I thought you were some creepy old guy

1711
01:55:20,160 --> 01:55:21,160
trying to hit on me.

1712
01:55:24,960 --> 01:55:25,960
Sorry for scaring you.

1713
01:55:26,480 --> 01:55:27,520
I apologize.

1714
01:55:27,840 --> 01:55:28,840
No problem.

1715
01:55:31,240 --> 01:55:32,320
You were leaving.

1716
01:55:33,240 --> 01:55:34,800
Were you planning to tail me?

1717
01:55:44,000 --> 01:55:45,200
All by yourself?

1718
01:55:46,760 --> 01:55:47,760
Pardon?

1719
01:55:48,000 --> 01:55:49,160
What are you talking about?

1720
01:55:51,080 --> 01:55:52,080
A few days ago

1721
01:55:53,120 --> 01:55:54,120
you were at Wynn.

1722
01:55:55,080 --> 01:55:56,560
You were with a boy.

1723
01:56:00,720 --> 01:56:01,720
Where's that boy now?

1724
01:56:08,160 --> 01:56:09,160
Dead.

1725
01:56:10,360 --> 01:56:11,360
Broke up?

1726
01:56:12,240 --> 01:56:13,760
Didn't you hear me?

1727
01:56:16,120 --> 01:56:17,440
He's dead.

1728
01:56:18,040 --> 01:56:19,040
Team two.

1729
01:56:19,080 --> 01:56:20,376
Seal Ponte Cais de Coloane
and R. Dos Navegantes.

1730
01:56:20,400 --> 01:56:22,880
Team three, take Entre-Campos,
Cordoaria and Cheoc Van.

1731
01:56:26,240 --> 01:56:28,040
He was killed in an LRT station.

1732
01:56:46,880 --> 01:56:48,360
That boy was a cop

1733
01:56:51,760 --> 01:56:53,520
and so are you. You're crazy.

1734
01:56:54,240 --> 01:56:55,560
Get away from me.

1735
01:56:56,520 --> 01:56:57,520
Go away.

1736
01:57:06,160 --> 01:57:07,840
You've managed to stall me.

1737
01:57:08,680 --> 01:57:09,680
You're pretty good.

1738
01:57:24,120 --> 01:57:25,120
Guoguo.

1739
01:57:27,120 --> 01:57:28,160
Call an ambulance.

1740
01:57:28,240 --> 01:57:29,240
Police.

1741
01:57:31,000 --> 01:57:32,280
Get out of here.

1742
01:57:46,280 --> 01:57:47,760
Please use the front door.

1743
01:58:45,720 --> 01:58:47,760
My West Lake vinegar fish.

1744
01:58:48,840 --> 01:58:49,840
Do you like it?

1745
01:58:54,080 --> 01:58:55,400
It sucked.

1746
01:58:57,120 --> 01:58:59,000
Go to hell.

1747
01:59:00,360 --> 01:59:01,880
Join me.

1748
02:01:21,320 --> 02:01:22,320
Come on.

1749
02:01:30,440 --> 02:01:31,440
C'mon.

1750
02:02:15,840 --> 02:02:16,840
Guoguo.

1751
02:02:52,320 --> 02:02:53,000
Are you all right?

1752
02:02:53,080 --> 02:02:54,240
It's not deep.

1753
02:02:54,280 --> 02:02:55,280
I'll be fine.

1754
02:02:57,160 --> 02:02:57,920
The ambulance is almost here.

1755
02:02:58,000 --> 02:02:59,400
Earpiece is in the pocket.

1756
02:03:00,880 --> 02:03:01,960
Guoguo, go after him.

1757
02:03:04,440 --> 02:03:05,200
Target headed out front door.

1758
02:03:05,320 --> 02:03:06,600
Wig and black jacket.

1759
02:03:07,240 --> 02:03:08,240
I'm going after him.

1760
02:03:33,680 --> 02:03:34,696
Piggy, he's heading north.

1761
02:03:34,720 --> 02:03:36,280
There's no surveillance in the alley.

1762
02:03:36,360 --> 02:03:37,560
You have to find him yourself.

1763
02:03:43,360 --> 02:03:44,520
Possible suspect sighting.

1764
02:03:48,360 --> 02:03:49,360
It's not the Shadow.

1765
02:03:53,760 --> 02:03:54,720
The roads are a mess

1766
02:03:54,760 --> 02:03:55,640
I can't find him.

1767
02:03:55,680 --> 02:03:57,040
Qiuguo, stay calm.

1768
02:03:58,280 --> 02:03:59,280
Get it together.

1769
02:04:04,480 --> 02:04:05,480
I can't find him.

1770
02:04:08,480 --> 02:04:10,200
Piggy, backup's almost there.

1771
02:04:10,280 --> 02:04:11,280
He can't be far.

1772
02:04:11,320 --> 02:04:12,320
You got this.

1773
02:04:17,760 --> 02:04:19,880
Remember the key points of tracking?

1774
02:04:19,960 --> 02:04:20,960
He Qiuguo?

1775
02:04:22,240 --> 02:04:22,920
Watch

1776
02:04:22,960 --> 02:04:23,960
and memorize.

1777
02:04:24,040 --> 02:04:25,040
You only get one glance.

1778
02:04:25,400 --> 02:04:26,440
Focus on key points.

1779
02:04:27,000 --> 02:04:28,080
All by yourself?

1780
02:04:30,640 --> 02:04:31,640
Memorize.

1781
02:04:32,280 --> 02:04:33,680
Memorize actively first.

1782
02:04:33,880 --> 02:04:34,720
Where's the boy?

1783
02:04:34,800 --> 02:04:36,240
Over time... Broke up?

1784
02:04:36,320 --> 02:04:38,720
You'll start to memorize subconsciously.

1785
02:04:45,600 --> 02:04:47,120
Go after him.

1786
02:04:50,080 --> 02:04:51,080
Hand.

1787
02:04:56,880 --> 02:04:57,880
Bandage.

1788
02:05:15,600 --> 02:05:16,720
Target spotted. I got him.

1789
02:05:16,840 --> 02:05:17,320
Where are you?

1790
02:05:17,400 --> 02:05:18,640
An alley south on R. Do Meio

1791
02:05:18,760 --> 02:05:19,600
Wu, prepare for arrest.

1792
02:05:19,760 --> 02:05:20,760
We're here.

1793
02:05:25,120 --> 02:05:27,240
Sir, you can't take painkillers like that.

1794
02:05:28,600 --> 02:05:29,600
Guoguo.

1795
02:05:30,160 --> 02:05:31,160
You got this.

1796
02:05:34,520 --> 02:05:35,520
Wait.

1797
02:05:36,240 --> 02:05:37,040
Qiuguo

1798
02:05:37,120 --> 02:05:39,320
if I set a trap at the Chapel of
St. Francis Xavier

1799
02:05:39,360 --> 02:05:40,480
can you send him this way?

1800
02:05:41,120 --> 02:05:42,960
Captain, I can't do this alone.

1801
02:05:43,800 --> 02:05:44,800
I need my team support.

1802
02:05:44,840 --> 02:05:46,000
I need the Surveillance Team.

1803
02:05:46,240 --> 02:05:47,760
Piggy. Miss us?

1804
02:05:50,320 --> 02:05:51,720
Central, Pork Bun is in position.

1805
02:05:51,800 --> 02:05:52,800
I'm at your 8 o'clock.

1806
02:05:52,920 --> 02:05:54,480
Potsticker in position. Parallel street

1807
02:05:54,560 --> 02:05:55,360
3 o' clock.

1808
02:05:55,440 --> 02:05:56,280
Eggy in position.

1809
02:05:56,360 --> 02:05:57,040
Tofu in position.

1810
02:05:57,160 --> 02:05:58,680
9 o'clock, next street over.

1811
02:06:03,000 --> 02:06:04,120
Calling Animal Paradise

1812
02:06:04,200 --> 02:06:05,200
Doghead is safe.

1813
02:06:08,720 --> 02:06:10,120
Rice Noodle in position. 2 o'clock.

1814
02:06:10,400 --> 02:06:12,280
I've studied and analyzed Shadow's habits.

1815
02:06:12,360 --> 02:06:15,280
From the current point,
there are 165 possible escape routes.

1816
02:06:15,440 --> 02:06:18,760
17 of them reach the
Chapel of St. Francis Xavier.

1817
02:06:19,680 --> 02:06:20,440
Pudding in position.

1818
02:06:20,520 --> 02:06:21,520
Right behind you.

1819
02:06:21,600 --> 02:06:22,560
Lucky in position.

1820
02:06:22,600 --> 02:06:23,600
Directly ahead of target.

1821
02:06:23,760 --> 02:06:25,840
Coordinates and directions
are sent to the team.

1822
02:06:25,960 --> 02:06:27,336
I will continue calculating
his route choices

1823
02:06:27,360 --> 02:06:28,120
and you will be updated.

1824
02:06:28,200 --> 02:06:29,336
Doghead calling Animal Paradise.

1825
02:06:29,360 --> 02:06:31,080
Adorable Unit's on-site.

1826
02:06:32,960 --> 02:06:34,040
Alpaca in position.

1827
02:06:36,840 --> 02:06:38,000
Calling Animal Paradise.

1828
02:06:40,160 --> 02:06:41,160
Piggy in position.

1829
02:06:41,200 --> 02:06:42,360
Attention, Adorable Unit.

1830
02:06:42,440 --> 02:06:43,696
Chapel of St. Francis Xavier Square

1831
02:06:43,720 --> 02:06:44,880
is about 280 meters northwest

1832
02:06:44,960 --> 02:06:46,760
of the target's current location.

1833
02:06:47,280 --> 02:06:47,920
The Shadow's injured.

1834
02:06:48,080 --> 02:06:49,160
He values his life.

1835
02:06:49,240 --> 02:06:50,800
All he wants right now is to flee.

1836
02:06:50,960 --> 02:06:52,720
He won't risk getting shot to harm you.

1837
02:06:53,400 --> 02:06:54,160
Adorable Unit.

1838
02:06:54,240 --> 02:06:55,600
You're the hounds now.

1839
02:06:56,160 --> 02:06:57,400
Round up and hunt.

1840
02:08:12,960 --> 02:08:14,160
Don't move.

1841
02:08:18,960 --> 02:08:19,960
Hands on your head.

1842
02:08:40,720 --> 02:08:41,720
I'm fine.

1843
02:08:53,080 --> 02:08:54,080
I'm a cop.

1844
02:08:54,320 --> 02:08:55,320
Fu Longsheng

1845
02:08:55,600 --> 02:08:56,600
you're under arrest.

1846
02:09:00,400 --> 02:09:01,400
Madam

1847
02:09:02,040 --> 02:09:03,640
He Qiuguo.

1848
02:09:05,800 --> 02:09:07,280
You made this happen.

1849
02:09:08,640 --> 02:09:09,840
You cuff me.

1850
02:09:20,560 --> 02:09:21,560
What's so funny?

1851
02:09:22,680 --> 02:09:24,000
You really can fight.

1852
02:09:24,200 --> 02:09:25,200
Shut up.

1853
02:09:26,080 --> 02:09:27,080
Guoguo.

1854
02:09:39,360 --> 02:09:40,240
Command central

1855
02:09:40,360 --> 02:09:42,200
we have Fu Longsheng in custody.

1856
02:09:49,080 --> 02:09:50,080
Well done.

1857
02:09:50,800 --> 02:09:52,480
Your parents would be very proud.

1858
02:09:57,000 --> 02:09:58,000
Sir.

1859
02:10:00,360 --> 02:10:01,840
Requesting to join the interrogation.

1860
02:10:02,120 --> 02:10:02,960
Aren't you on leave?

1861
02:10:03,040 --> 02:10:04,360
Requesting to terminate my leave.

1862
02:10:06,640 --> 02:10:08,800
I do miss work.

1863
02:10:09,800 --> 02:10:12,000
We'll be needing your help in the future.

1864
02:10:13,120 --> 02:10:14,280
I've already taught them

1865
02:10:14,640 --> 02:10:16,240
everything I know.

1866
02:10:17,320 --> 02:10:18,320
I'm going back

1867
02:10:18,360 --> 02:10:19,960
to my retirement.

1868
02:10:21,280 --> 02:10:22,960
Go to the hospital first.

1869
02:10:35,320 --> 02:10:37,000
Ready. Action.

1870
02:10:46,720 --> 02:10:48,440
What should we do? Go!

1871
02:10:48,480 --> 02:10:49,600
You go fight them out there.

1872
02:10:54,560 --> 02:10:55,560
Let me tell you...

1873
02:10:55,920 --> 02:10:57,760
We... you all...

1874
02:11:02,520 --> 02:11:04,520
Piggy, X Target…

1875
02:11:04,960 --> 02:11:05,960
X Target...

1876
02:11:07,080 --> 02:11:08,640
I will try to talk them into...

1877
02:11:09,240 --> 02:11:10,560
I will try to persuade...

1878
02:11:26,760 --> 02:11:28,080
Simon could see you.

1879
02:11:30,600 --> 02:11:32,240
For your shot...

1880
02:11:32,480 --> 02:11:33,600
You have taken a seat.

1881
02:11:37,440 --> 02:11:38,800
One, two, three.

1882
02:11:43,360 --> 02:11:45,280
When I turned around...

1883
02:11:50,480 --> 02:11:53,720
In dreams of love

1884
02:11:54,160 --> 02:11:57,360
a promise through three lifetimes.

1885
02:11:57,440 --> 02:12:00,760
How can one bear to seek the truth?

1886
02:12:00,840 --> 02:12:01,840
Awesome.

1887
02:12:04,720 --> 02:12:05,720
I'm fine.

1888
02:12:14,000 --> 02:12:15,520
Hey, how come you behaved like that?

1889
02:12:16,400 --> 02:12:17,000
Are you all right?

1890
02:12:17,080 --> 02:12:18,120
I've to go to the hospital

1891
02:12:34,680 --> 02:12:36,000
Just stick a plaster over.

1892
02:12:39,000 --> 02:12:40,000
I'm fine.

1893
02:12:42,720 --> 02:12:44,200
Thank him.

1894
02:12:53,280 --> 02:12:54,960
Very nice.

1895
02:12:55,040 --> 02:12:56,160
Very nice.

1896
02:13:01,280 --> 02:13:02,440
This is okay.

1897
02:13:03,640 --> 02:13:04,640
Power

1898
02:13:05,040 --> 02:13:06,680
Jackie Chan Power.

1899
02:13:07,280 --> 02:13:09,280
You guys think I am old and useless?

1900
02:13:09,360 --> 02:13:10,280
We didn't!

1901
02:13:10,360 --> 02:13:11,360
We wouldn't dare.

1902
02:13:11,560 --> 02:13:13,520
I think you can still fight
for another 20 years.

1903
02:13:13,600 --> 02:13:14,600
20 years.

1904
02:13:14,800 --> 02:13:15,960
That's too brutal.

1905
02:13:23,680 --> 02:13:24,680
Officer Wong.

1906
02:13:25,920 --> 02:13:27,280
Why are we meeting here?

1907
02:13:27,800 --> 02:13:28,880
We found a lead.

1908
02:13:28,960 --> 02:13:30,160
That hacker, Simon

1909
02:13:30,320 --> 02:13:32,280
had help from someone much more capable.

1910
02:13:32,640 --> 02:13:33,800
My people thought so too.

1911
02:13:34,160 --> 02:13:35,400
We checked his computer.

1912
02:13:35,480 --> 02:13:37,360
There is no hacking
source code in his devices.

1913
02:13:38,000 --> 02:13:39,360
The more important question is

1914
02:13:39,400 --> 02:13:40,320
why did this mastermind

1915
02:13:40,400 --> 02:13:42,800
deliberately leave loopholes
for my people to find?

1916
02:13:44,040 --> 02:13:45,040
Wait.

1917
02:13:46,400 --> 02:13:48,240
I know who my people are.

1918
02:13:49,840 --> 02:13:51,720
Your people are...

1919
02:13:53,920 --> 02:13:54,920
Right now

1920
02:13:55,360 --> 02:13:56,680
you don't have the clearance yet.

1921
02:13:58,160 --> 02:14:00,840
Aren't you just a retired dog walker?

1922
02:14:00,880 --> 02:14:03,040
You sound like you have a secret identity.

1923
02:14:03,240 --> 02:14:04,640
Fragile.

1924
02:14:06,120 --> 02:14:07,600
Lucky.

1925
02:14:09,240 --> 02:14:10,920
Relax.

1926
02:14:12,600 --> 02:14:14,200
Energy.

1927
02:14:16,400 --> 02:14:17,840
Target.

1928
02:14:19,240 --> 02:14:20,600
Amateur.

1929
02:14:21,800 --> 02:14:23,240
Family.

1930
02:14:24,560 --> 02:14:25,760
Shadow.

1931
02:14:27,400 --> 02:14:29,080
Betrayal.

1932
02:14:30,600 --> 02:14:31,920
Grateful.

1933
02:14:33,920 --> 02:14:35,360
Blind.

1934
02:15:32,520 --> 02:15:33,840
Escalate.

